<item>
 <title>Shalom Asalaam</title>
 <link>https://vse.la/jaya-lakshmi/shalom-asalaam</link>
 <description>&lt;div class=&quot;field field-name-body field-type-text-with-summary field-label-hidden&quot;&gt;
    &lt;div class=&quot;field-items&quot;&gt;
          &lt;div class=&quot;field-item even&quot;&gt;&lt;p&gt;WHISPERS:&lt;br /&gt;
Shalom &lt;br /&gt;
Asalaam&lt;/p&gt;

&lt;p&gt;VERSE 1:&lt;br /&gt;
Since the dawn of time&lt;br /&gt;
We&#039;ve been waging wars&lt;br /&gt;
And hiding our love behind locked doors&lt;br /&gt;
Using fear to dominate &amp;amp; control&lt;br /&gt;
We&#039;ve been fighting against, our very own soul&lt;/p&gt;

&lt;p&gt;VERSE 2:&lt;br /&gt;
Now we stand on the brink of a new frontier&lt;br /&gt;
And the power of peace is becoming clear&lt;br /&gt;
It&#039;s going to take all our courage to make a new start&lt;br /&gt;
It&#039;s going to take a revolution of the heart&lt;/p&gt;

&lt;p&gt;CHORUS:&lt;br /&gt;
Shalom alackhem (&quot;Live In Peace&quot; In Hebrew)&lt;br /&gt;
Asalaam a-ley-khoom (&quot;Live In Peace&quot; In Arabic)&lt;br /&gt;
Shalom alackhem&lt;br /&gt;
Asalaam a-ley-khoom, yaeh&lt;/p&gt;

&lt;p&gt;VERSE 3:&lt;br /&gt;
It&#039;s a new kind of freedom&lt;br /&gt;
We&#039;ve never known before &lt;br /&gt;
A deeper understanding&lt;br /&gt;
Because we know a lot more &lt;br /&gt;
We just keep going&lt;br /&gt;
We don&#039;t look back &lt;br /&gt;
Stay focused on the light&lt;br /&gt;
And you&#039;ll stay on track&lt;/p&gt;

&lt;p&gt;VERSE 4:&lt;br /&gt;
It&#039;s a new kind of love &lt;br /&gt;
Stronger than before &lt;br /&gt;
Flowing like a river&lt;br /&gt;
Right to the core &lt;br /&gt;
We&#039;re finding our freedom&lt;br /&gt;
We&#039;re finding our peace &lt;br /&gt;
We&#039;ll find it together &lt;br /&gt;
And the wars will cease&lt;/p&gt;

&lt;p&gt;WHISPERS:&lt;br /&gt;
Shalom&lt;br /&gt;
Asalaam&lt;/p&gt;

&lt;p&gt;CHORUS:&lt;br /&gt;
Shalom alackhem &lt;br /&gt;
Asalaam a-ley-khoom &lt;br /&gt;
Shalom alackhem&lt;br /&gt;
Asalaam a-ley-khoom, yaeh&lt;/p&gt;

&lt;p&gt;WHISPERS:&lt;br /&gt;
It&#039;s going to take a revolution of the heart&lt;br /&gt;
A revolution of the heart&lt;/p&gt;
